name: Prabhat Agro
overview:
Year of Establishment 2007 We introduce our selves as one of the leading manufacturer of Turbine Pump operated by oil engine & electric motor for open well & tube well with the range of 40 to 350 feet in four different size. V6 & V8, V10 & V12 with the column pipe (GI)of 3 & 4 inch.

Our Products /; Vertical Turbine Pump Deep Well Turbine Pump Agriculture Turbine Pump V12 Turbine Pump V6 Turbine Pump V10 Turbine Pump V8 Turbine Pump Agricultural Equipment Openwell Turbine Pump Turbine Pump Head

Our Quality: We lay special emphasis on the quality of our products, as we are an ISO 9001:2008 certified co. indulged in manufacturing and supplying a wide range of Turbine Pumps to our clients.

Client Satisfaction: We are known to be client oriented organizations, who are engaged in manufacturing and supplying a qualitative range of Turbine Pumps To attain maximum client satisfaction, we offer our clients the best quality products that are known for high functionality, easy installation, low maintenance, longer service life, low energy consumption and high strength.

Our Infrastructure: We have sophisticated and modern infrastructure facility at our premises, which is installed with high tech machines, cutting edge technology and is spread over a sprawling area.

Why Us?: Some of the factors, which gives us a competitive edge over other market players are:

• Premium quality products • Capacious warehouse • Wide distribution network
